{"tid":1865146,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"柒婆究竟有甚麼病？ - 高慧然","createTime":"2020-02-06T04:30:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T05:04:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"89f941c7aaf883d14b37ffcdaf8af88aa245329b","tid":1865146,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:30:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20200206/20856881/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200206%2F20856881%2F&d=N89%2BOK2GKuUyahfhaKnAsvvW7D1Q%2FvztR01HWodNoCE%3D&h=c90d1d67\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200206%2F20856881%2F&h=f7102979\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20200206/20856881/</a><br />\n<br />\n柒婆究竟有甚麼病？ - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200206/large/1580885184_267c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200206%2Flarge%2F1580885184_267c.jpg&h=9eda5c80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫護大罷工，理由和目的說得清清楚楚，不是為了自己的安危，而是要求政府源頭截止疫症散播，是為了讓岌岌可危的本港醫療系統不致崩潰，是為了救治更多病人，是為了全體香港人的健康福祉，是為了守護香港。<br />\n<br />\n可是柒婆怎麼回應？她冷笑，她污衊醫護人員挾持政府，她一口拒絕醫護人員的訴求，說他們「不會得逞」。世上怎麼會有這樣的人？作為地區行政長官，保障轄內居民健康是她的職責，她失職了，有人提醒她，她就決定跟對方鬥。<br />\n<br />\n這不是一個正常的地區行政長官應有的反應吧？這會不會是一種病？當然，我不是醫生，我無法判斷。我只能用我的生活經驗去比較，迄今為止，我從未見過一個人，是如此全無理性，缺乏常識，藐視專業意見，亦無道德，更漠視個人職業所要求的職業操守、原則與守則，以一己之喜好為標準，竭盡偏執之能事，為鬥而鬥，不顧及任何後果。<br />\n<br />\n一個自稱對自己有要求，考不到「第一名」會痛哭的所謂高材生，跟對岸的台灣總統蔡英文比比，再跟澳門新上任的特首賀一誠比比，輸得一敗塗地。人家專心抗疫，抵抗的是外來的瘟疫，她卻把所有抗疫者視作敵人，把抗疫戰變成對香港人的政治批鬥。原來這就是所謂「好打得」，天生嗜打。這個人，究竟有沒有病？若有，是一種甚麼樣的病？ <br />\n<br />\n高慧然<br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk"},{"pid":"276fcdeac17143f8957d8a316c033cba334ad0a0","tid":1865146,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:35:49.000Z","msg":"聽講佢會考分數好唔掂喎"},{"pid":"1dc1caf3048f5199172cf19b44dc5962af970f59","tid":1865146,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:44:06.000Z","msg":"攬炒啦, 等全世界封香港"},{"pid":"ead924c1ed15ed4c81e98bfe4b5ea0dda1d8cfb9","tid":1865146,"uid":153239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"276fcdeac17143f8957d8a316c033cba334ad0a0","tid":1865146,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:35:49.000Z","msg":"聽講佢會考分數好唔掂喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:45:29.000Z","msg":"好似得3A咋啵! 重過係失手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bccf75c9ac28ce82289642c24fc75d1a8852fb2","tid":1865146,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ead924c1ed15ed4c81e98bfe4b5ea0dda1d8cfb9","tid":1865146,"uid":153239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"276fcdeac17143f8957d8a316c033cba334ad0a0","tid":1865146,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:35:49.000Z","msg":"聽講佢會考分數好唔掂喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:45:29.000Z","msg":"好似得3A咋啵! 重過係失手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:47:41.000Z","msg":"28<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但會考都拎黎打飛機<br />\n係咪on9?"},{"pid":"bade7925faf66215998bbe8b3aea67b92dd95aa4","tid":1865146,"uid":288523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:52:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ebe2afc59fce4a58157dd30e91ec0f6650ed3c23","tid":1865146,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T05:04:08.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa